why does he not act on this friendship ? 
our best friends in the world are the citizens of the United States of America . 
we are not too small to criticize them . 
we do it all the time . 
why can we not do the same with China ? 
why this special treatment of the Chinese government ? 
why is the Chinese government so committed to forcefully keeping Chinese citizens within the country ' s borders ? 
honourable senators , this past summer , few short weeks after Senator Austin assured this chamber that China had changed for the better , the Chinese government arrested more than 30,000 of its citizens . 
since then , it has continued to arrest more . 
their crime ? 
according to the Chinese government - and , I presume , Senator Wilson ' s religious partners as well - it was belonging to the Falun Gong spiritual movement I mentioned a minute ago . 
