my criticism is directed at the Chinese government , not the people of China . 
the Prime Minister says Canada cannot make a difference . 
why , then , is his government telling the world it thinks human rights are important ? 
it is one of the fundamental objectives . 
are not human rights part of Canada ' s values ? 
obviously the answer is " yes " . 
